WEBVTT

00:00.746 --> 00:02.001
Sir, you wanted to see me?

00:02.003 --> 00:03.495
Yes,
I have an assignment for you.

00:03.539 --> 00:04.757
I'm afraid it's not
a pleasant one.

00:04.801 --> 00:06.542
Oh, my God.
Please tell me it's not...

00:06.585 --> 00:09.022
Yes, it's Hitchcock related.

00:09.066 --> 00:10.372
Son of a bitch.

00:10.415 --> 00:13.157
Detective Hitchcock is set to
testify in court this afternoon.

00:13.201 --> 00:16.465
It's an important case, and I'd rather
not get another call from the DA

00:16.508 --> 00:19.424
saying he showed up
"covered in condiments."

00:19.468 --> 00:21.201
So you want me to
keep Hitchcock from

00:21.226 --> 00:23.254
spilling on himself for
the rest of the day?

00:23.298 --> 00:24.560
We both know that's impossible.

00:24.603 --> 00:26.344
- I'm counting on you.
- I won't do it.

00:26.388 --> 00:28.955
- There's nobody else I trust.
- What you're asking is insane.

00:28.999 --> 00:31.393
- I'm not asking.
- It's a suicide mission!

00:31.436 --> 00:33.221
- Then prepare for death.
- You've lost your mind!

00:33.264 --> 00:35.658
This is a direct order,
Detective! Get in line!

00:35.701 --> 00:37.616
Hey.
You guys startled Hitchcock.

00:37.660 --> 00:40.532
He spilled two full jars
of spaghetti sauce on himself.

00:40.576 --> 00:42.015
Thanks a lot, fellas.

